#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.17"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.17:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.17:0.2"
msgid "2. Dhammacakkappavattanavagga"
msgstr "2. Rolling Forth the Wheel of Dhamma"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.17:0.3"
msgid "17. Avijjāsutta"
msgstr "17. Ignorance"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.17:1.1"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated to one side, that mendicant said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.2"
msgid "“‘avijjā, avijjā’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr "“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘ignorance’."

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.3"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, bhante, avijjā;"
msgstr "What is ignorance?"

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.4"
msgid "kittāvatā ca avijjāgato hotī”ti?"
msgstr "And how is an ignorant person defined?”"

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ kho, bhikkhu, dukkhe aññāṇaṃ, dukkhasamudaye aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhe "
"aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya aññāṇaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"“Not knowing about suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of "
"suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhu, avijjā;"
msgstr "This is called ignorance."

msgctxt "sn56.17:1.7"
msgid "ettāvatā ca avijjāgato hotīti."
msgstr "And this is how an ignorant person is defined."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.17:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhu, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.17:2.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
